  <m0>(box) <m0>The Birdcage <m0>(R) (--) <m0>There's no explicit sex, but because of this movie's adult subject matter and language (--) one of the main characters owns a drag club in South Beach (--) this is best for older teens, who'll enjoy the silliness and maybe learn a thing or two about acceptance.<ql>
