<m0>   (box) Celtic Pride<m0> <m0>(PG-13)<m0> (--) Mike O'Hara (Daniel Stern) and Jimmy Flaherty (Dan Aykroyd), two rabid Boston Celtics fans masquerading as dumb and dumber, kidnap Lewis Scott (Damon Wayans), an arrogant, ice-cool, ball-hogging Utah Jazz star, to keep him from playing in the championship game. But Scott escapes, threatening to send his kidnappers to jail unless they root for the Jazz. The movie clearly is aimed for young kids, but it is not appropriate for them, with its profanity and fisticuffs.<ep>
