<m0>  <m0>(box) Primal Fear<m0> (R)<m0> (--) <m1> <m0>This is an intense, adult drama, with nudity, profanity and adult issues. Martin Vail (Richard Gere) is a hotshot defense lawyer for Aaron (Edward Norton), a runaway accused of murdering a sexually abusive archbishop in Chicago. When the case goes to trial, Vail discovers that Aaron isn't what he appears to be.<ql>
